data.description: You must see this one!!! Completely remodeled brick home. Carpet replaced, crown molding, freshly painted in great colors, new woodwork & Windows, 3 bedrooms, 1 1/2 bath, ceiling fans, side x side frig with water & ice in door, stainless sink, upgraded nickel fixtures, elec. oven range, microwave vent hood, central heat and air, large inside laundry room, one car attached garage, large back yard with wood privacy fence. Roof recently replaced. Call for appointment to view.
